                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8034" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0083</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4302 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">强制还是助推：哈啰解决共享单车违停乱放之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Stick or Nudge: The Way for Hellobike to Solve Disorderly Parking of Shared Bicycles</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王雅璨，苏端，詹紫琳，胡雅梅（通讯作者），曾德麟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海钧正网络科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享单车；奖励；惩罚；助推 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shared bicycles, Reward, Punishment, Nudge</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享单车由于其经济便利、绿色环保的特性在国内迅速发展，但也带来了单车违停乱放、堆积占道等现象，给城市治理带来挑战，阻碍了共享经济的可持续发展。本案例讲述共享单车企业哈啰如何不断地摸索与创新用户行为干预手段，以解决单车违停乱放问题。本案例全面分析哈啰所采用的奖励、惩罚、奖惩结合、助推等多种强制与非强制管理举措，特别借助于行为经济学与其中的助推理论深入剖析助推手段背后的内涵、机理与效果，并提出了设计与创新助推手段的EAST行为干预框架。这为哈啰进一步创新自己的助推手段、为其他企业与现代化行业解决类似问题提供了有益启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Due to its economical, convenient and pro-environmental characteristics, shared bicycles have developed rapidly in China. However, it also brings phenomena including disorderly parking, stacking and occupying roads, which pose challenges to urban governance and hinders the sustainable development of shared economy. This case describes how the bike-sharing enterprise, Hellobike, explores and innovates users’ behavioral intervention methods continuously to alleviate disorderly parking. This case comprehensively analyzes various mandatory and non-mandatory measures of Hellobike including reward, punishment, the combination of reward and punishment, and nudges. Specifically, behavioral economics and nudging theory are used to deeply analyze the connotation, mechanism, and effects of nudges. And the behavioral intervention framework of EAST is used to design and innovate nudges.  The implications for Hellobike to further innovate its nudging measures and for other enterprises to solve similar issues are finally provided.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理经济学》、《行为经济学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外部性理论；公地悲剧；助推理论；经济人与社会人；有限理性</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
